N2  - The article presents a calendar of meetings involving the Academy of Management from 1963 to 1964. The Eastern Management Association meeting was held on May 15 and 16, 1964. The Southern Division of the Academy of Management held its annual meeting with the Southern Economic Association at Roanoke, Virginia in November 1963. The 11th Annual Institute of the American Society of Training Directors will be held August 2?7 and August 9?14, 1964. The Institute of Management Sciences and the Operations Research Society of America will hold a joint national meeting from October 7?9, 1964 at the Hotel Leamington in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
